Property.Name: QueryScript
Property.Value: SELECT f.Id,f.AUC, d.Date DateDate,d.Day DateDay,d.DayInMonth DateDayInMonth,d.Month DateMonth,d.MonthName DateMonthName,d.Year DateYear,d.DayOfWeek DateDayOfWeek,d.DayOfWeekName DateDayOfWeekName,d.Weekday DateWeekday,d.MonthInYear DateMonthInYear,d.Quarter DateQuarter,d.QuarterInYear DateQuarterInYear, m.Abbreviation MuscleAbbreviation,m.Name MuscleName, p.Id PatientId,p.PatientId PatientPatientId,p.Name PatientName,p.Sex PatientSex,p.BornOn PatientBornOn,p.DiagnosedOn PatientDiagnosedOn, t.Hour TimeHour,t.TimeOfDay TimeTimeOfDay FROM dbo.Fact f INNER JOIN dbo.D_Date d on d.Id=f.DateId INNER JOIN dbo.D_Muscle m on m.Id=f.MuscleId INNER JOIN dbo.D_Patient p on p.Id=f.PatientId INNER JOIN dbo.D_Time t on t.Id=f.TimeId
